      "title": "Afghan quake death toll rises to more than 1,150",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The death toll from a magnitude 6.1 earthquake in eastern Afghanistan has risen to more than 1,150, according to the Bakhtar News Agency.",
        "A second earthquake shook the region of Paktika in Afghanistan at around 10.00 am local time on Friday, killing at least five people, local media reported."
      ],
